grid.title: Fire Wet Trees
grid.author: Cell Society Team 5
grid.description: This configuration shows a Sugar grid for users to create their own layout. Click on a cell to cycle through its states (Yellow = Open, Green = Tree, Red = Fire). The Catch Probability is 0.5 (50%) by default. First pause the simulation, change cells to the desired values, save the configuration, then reload the configuration. Now you can reset the simulation any time.
